}
```

**Estrutura do summary final:**
```json
{
    "experiment_config": { ... },
    "rounds": [
        {"round": 1, "accuracy": 0.45, "loss": 1.23},
        ...
    ],
    "final_accuracy": 0.67,
    "final_loss": 0.89
